summary: This is an FBI criminal history record response from the New York State Division of Criminal Justice Services to an inquiry. It indicates the subject has a record based on fingerprint comparisons, includes a DNA indicator stating 'DNA NOT IN CODIS - COLLECT DNA', and contains no transmitted fingerprint images. The record is marked as official use only.

persons.name: Michael C. Green
persons.role: Executive Deputy Commissioner of the NYS Division of Criminal Justice Services
persons.context: He is listed as the executive deputy commissioner of the agency providing the FBI record response.

events.title: FBI Criminal History Record Response
events.description: The New York State Division of Criminal Justice Services provides an FBI criminal history record in response to an inquiry. The record is based on fingerprint comparisons and includes a DNA indicator.

locations: Alfred E. Smith Building, 80 South Swan St. Albany, New York 12210
keyFacts: The document is an official FBI criminal history record response dated October 6, 2021.
The record is based on fingerprint comparisons and pertains to a single individual (subject not named in provided text).
It contains a DNA indicator stating 'DNA NOT IN CODIS - COLLECT DNA'.
No fingerprint images were transmitted with this record.
The use of the record is regulated by law and for official use only.
